      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "width": 560,
      "height": 260,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Document / Publishing Library\n\nThis package preserves authored document structure without flattening everything into markdown blobs.\n\nV1 classes:\n- `section`\n- `reference`\n- `figure`\n- `embed`\n- `annotation`\n- `document-summary` (labelled `Summary`)\n\nDeferred for later:\n- `callout`\n- `quote`\n- `footnote`\n- `toc-anchor`",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
