    {
      "id": "document-publishing-root-note",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Publishing Pressures",
      "position": {
        "x": 1040,
        "y": 220
      },
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "width": 460,
      "height": 240,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Publishing Pressures\n\nLikely structural relationships:\n- `section` contains document fragments\n- `annotation` attaches to `section`, `reference`, or `figure`\n- `Summary` rolls up a document region\n\nRuntime/export pressure:\n- ordering and nesting\n- portable embeds\n- reference resolution\n- export targets that preserve structure",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
